data.description: This charming single-story home is situated on a large corner lot, with a functional and convenient floor plan. The galley kitchen provides plenty of countertop space and cabinet storage. The bedrooms are generously sized, and the master bedroom has an en suite bathroom. One of the highlights of this home is the covered patio with a fireplace, perfect for outdoor entertaining or simply enjoying a cozy evening with family and friends. The expansive backyard is a blank canvas with endless potential, allowing for the creation of your dream outdoor oasis. There is a large shed for additional storage and mature fruit trees and lush landscaping. The home is in a great location, with close proximity to schools, parks, shopping centers, restaurants, and freeway access. Don’t miss this wonderful opportunity!
